```

### Rule 3: **Add Missing Tests**
```ruby
# If tests don't exist for your changes, ADD them
# test/controllers/api/v1/users_controller_test.rb
class Api::V1::UsersControllerTest < ActionDispatch::IntegrationTest
  test "should create user with valid params" do
    post api_v1_users_url, params: { user: valid_user_params }
    assert_response :created
  end
  
  test "should reject user with invalid params" do
    post api_v1_users_url, params: { user: invalid_user_params }
    assert_response :unprocessable_entity
  end
end
```

### Rule 4: **Test-Driven Development When Possible**
```bash
# Write failing test first (if time allows)
rails test test/models/user_test.rb  # Should fail

# Implement feature
# Edit app/models/user.rb

# Test should now pass
rails test test/models/user_test.rb  # Should pass
```

